he scope pattern `\\\\?\\C:\\path\\to\\dir\\**`, we expect the scope to have:\n- `\\\\?\\C:\\path\\to\\dir\\**`\n- `C:\\path\\to\\dir\\**`\n\nbut if we use `dunce::simplified`, it will see `**` as invalid path component on Windows and will not simplify the path resulting in a scope that only has `\\\\?\\C:\\path\\to\\dir\\**`\n\n<!--\nBefore submitting a PR, please read https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri/blob/dev/.github/CONTRIBUTING.md#pull-request-guidelines\n\n1. Give the PR a descriptive title.\n\n  Examples of good title:\n    - fix(windows): fix race condition in event loop\n    - docs: update example for `App::show`\n    - feat: add `Window::set_fullscreen`\n\n  Examples of bad title:\n    - fix #7123\n    - update docs\n    - fix bugs\n\n2. If there is a related issue, reference it in the PR text, e.g. closes #123.\n3. If this change requires a new version, then add a change file in `.changes` directory with the appropriate bump, see https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri/blob/dev/.changes/README.md\n4. Ensure that all your commits are signed https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/managing-commit-signature-verification/signing-commits\n5. Ensure `cargo test` and `cargo clippy` passes.\n6. Propose your changes as a draft PR if your work is still in progress.\n-->\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tauri-apps/tauri/issues/11730/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":2,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tauri-apps/tauri/issues/11730/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":15356256228,"node_id":"CE_lADOC7lts86dZzCJzwAAAAOTTd_k","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/tauri-apps/tauri/issues/events/15356256228","actor":{"login":"amrbashir","id":48618675,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ4NjE4Njc1","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/48618675?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/amrbashir","ht